import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import {BrowserRouter} from "react-router-dom"

import App from "./App"
import {ThemeContextProvider} from "./themeContext"

ReactDOM.render(
    <ThemeContextProvider>
        <BrowserRouter>
            <App />
        </BrowserRouter>
    </ThemeContextProvider>
    , document.getElementById("root")
)
